From e45bb7fb92b6536d5462856e6c9bb93d8c70c955 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 6 Mar 2026 20:55:25 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: comprehensive UI/UX overhaul & critical bug fixes
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

PROFILE PAGE FIXES:
- Removed broken flash/error display, replaced with proper query-param-based toasts
- Added inline Change Password form with current-password verification, strength meter, and match validation
- Added show/hide password toggles to all password fields
- Avatar camera overlay button for quick photo change
- Fixed avatar update to properly reflect in sidebar immediately after upload
- Added Danger Zone section with email-based reset option
- Fixed profile info display (member since, email, role, verification status)

SIDEBAR FIXES:
- Sidebar footer now shows user avatar image (if set) instead of just initials
- Shows user email below name in sidebar footer
- Sidebar footer user area is now a clickable link to /profile
- Logout button styled in danger color for clarity

CSS & UI IMPROVEMENTS:
- Complete select/dropdown overhaul: custom indigo chevron, hover states, focus rings
- Priority selects: emoji icons (🟢🟡🔴🚨) for instant visual recognition
- Status selects: emoji icons (⬜🔄🔍✅) for instant visual recognition
- Better badge colors (urgent/high/medium/low) with proper borders
- Smooth page fade-in animation
- Improved dropdown menus with rounded items and hover colors
- Better scrollbar styling
- Project cards lift on hover
- File upload drag-area improvements
- Enhanced alert styles with borders
- Password strength bar on profile page
- Better member row styling
- Add-member form only visible to project owner
- Non-owners see informational message explaining owner-only permission

EMAIL TEMPLATE OVERHAUL:
- Completely rebuilt all 7 email templates with professional HTML
- Beautiful responsive design with gradient hero sections
- Per-email color themes (green=welcome, blue=verify, yellow=reset, etc.)
- Welcome email with feature stats grid
- Password reset with expiry info box and link fallback
- Task assigned with task+project info box
- Comment notification with reply CTA
- Daily digest with overdue task list and stats
- Production-grade responsive layout wrapper
- Proper preheader text for email clients

DASHBOARD:
- Greeting now shows user's first name: 'Welcome back, Tejash!'

PROJECT SHOW:
- Flash messages (success/error) now properly displayed
- Add Member section: clearer UI with helper text
- Non-owner gets informative locked message instead of hidden form

WEB ROUTES:
- resolveWebUser now fetches and exposes avatar field
- WebUser interface updated with optional avatar field
- Profile route now passes query params instead of flash object
- renderWithLayout supports currentPath override from locals
